@startuml Omni_AI_Sequence
title Omni AI - Global System Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant MongoDB
participant RAGService
participant S3
participant MLService

== LOGIN ==
User -> Frontend: Open App
Frontend -> Backend: POST /auth/login
Backend -> MongoDB: Query user
MongoDB --> Backend: User data
Backend -> Backend: Verify password
Backend --> Frontend: JWT token
Frontend --> User: Dashboard

== AI CHAT ==
User -> Frontend: Ask question
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/ai/ask
Backend -> RAGService: Generate response
RAGService -> MongoDB: Search docs
MongoDB --> RAGService: Chunks
RAGService --> Backend: Response
Backend --> Frontend: Answer
Frontend --> User: Display

== TASKS ==
User -> Frontend: Create task
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/tasks
Backend -> MongoDB: Save
MongoDB --> Backend: Task ID
Backend --> Frontend: Success
Frontend --> User: Added

== FILE UPLOAD ==
User -> Frontend: Select file
Frontend -> Backend: POST /upload
Backend -> S3: Upload
S3 --> Backend: URL
Backend -> MongoDB: Metadata
Backend --> Frontend: Done
Frontend --> User: Uploaded

== FINANCE ==
User -> Frontend: Add expense
Frontend -> Backend: POST /finance
Backend -> MongoDB: Create
Backend -> MLService: Anomaly check
MLService --> Backend: Result
Backend --> Frontend: Success
Frontend --> User: Recorded

== ML PREDICT ==
User -> Frontend: Prediction
Frontend -> Backend: POST /predict
Backend -> MongoDB: Get history
Backend -> MLService: Analyze
MLService --> Backend: Results
Backend --> Frontend: Insights
Frontend --> User: Display

== SEARCH ==
User -> Frontend: Search
Frontend -> Backend: POST /search
Backend -> MongoDB: Query
MongoDB --> Backend: Results
Backend --> Frontend: List
Frontend --> User: Display

== LOGOUT ==
User -> Frontend: Logout
Frontend -> Backend: POST /logout
Backend -> MongoDB: Clear
MongoDB --> Backend: Done
Backend --> Frontend: Success
Frontend --> User: Login page

== AUTO-INDEX ==
Backend -> Backend: Start
Backend -> MongoDB: Index docs
MongoDB --> Backend: 2000 chunks
Backend -> Backend: Done

@enduml
